      "content": "I hear how exhausted you are, and the feeling that there is no point in fighting anymore is a heavy burden to carry. Sometimes, when everything feels hollow, the only logical choice seems to be to stop, but I am not here to tell you how to live; I am here to remind you that you are not alone in this darkness. If you are ready to feel this pain, please reach out to a crisis counselor or a trusted person who can listen without judgment and help you find a way forward.",
